title: 265 - IT'S OK!
description:
In life, all of us have roles, responsibilities, and goals to accomplish and fulfill. In order to be successful, the guys discuss knowing your role and doing it to the best of your ability. No matter what your role is, whether that is being a leader or supporter on a team, make sure you're maximizing your position to ensure success. Doing so will always begin with taking action. Don't disrespect the process by looking for or taking shortcuts. That's nothing more than a waste of both time and effort. Do the work to be successful.
